ects are expected to be operational by March 14. This success paves the way for potential central government funding for further city upgrades.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/smart-city/completion-of-smart-city-projects-in-uttar-pradesh-cities-paves-way-for-enhanced-urban-living/128957998?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-221806/128957998.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "smart-city"}]}